  Select Model and Effort
  Choose a DeepSeek model and reasoning level.

  1. deepseek-v4-pro (default)  Default Whale coding model for planning,
                                diagnosis, review, and verification.
  2. deepseek-v4-flash          Fast Whale coding model for low-latency
                                everyday implementation work.
  3. gpt-5.5                    Frontier model for complex coding, research,
                                and real-world work.
  4. gpt-5.4                    Strong model for everyday coding.
  5. gpt-5.4-mini               Small, fast, and cost-efficient model for
                                simpler coding tasks.
  6. gpt-5.3-codex              Coding-optimized model.
› 7. gpt-5.2 (current)          Optimized for professional work and long-
                                running agents.

  Press enter to select reasoning effort, or esc to dismiss.
